Package services

Class CampStaffService

java.lang.Object
services.CampStaffService
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICampStaffService
public class CampStaffService extends Object implements ICampStaffService
The CampStaffService class implements the ICampStaffService interface and provides methods for managing staff-related camp services. These services aid in the overall staffs' desired operations. Services include creating/deleting camps and toggling visibility.
